Description: Entity: This entity is the subject of a beneficial ownership relationship. One of `EntitytatementReference <#entitytatementreference>`__ or `EntityStatement <#entitystatement>`__

Interested party: The interested party has some level of ownership or control over the entity referenced in this beneficial ownership statement. One of `EntityStatement <#entitystatement>`__ or `PersonStatement <#personstatement>`__ or `NullParty <#nullparty>`__ or `EntityStatementReference <#entitystatementreference>`__ or `PersonStatementReference <#personstatementreference>`__
Interests: A describecription of the interests held by the interestedParty covered by this statement in the entity covered by this statement. See `Interest <#interest>`__ section for further details.
Source: The source of the information that links the entity and the interested party, or that supports a null statement. See `Source <#source>`__
